      <title>德州养老金将斥资 400 亿美元聘请私募市场投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/texas-pension-with-40-billion-to-hire-private-markets-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯市政退休系统 (Texas Municipal Retirement System) 规模 400 亿美元养老基金的首席投资官 Yup Kim 表示，该系统正在招聘三名投资人员，以期扩大其在私人市场的直接投资能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/texas-pension-with-40-billion-to-hire-private-markets-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达的盈利预期如何</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/what-to-expect-from-nvidia-earnings-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七巨头成员 Nvidia 将于周三公布财报，交易员们正准备迎接股价的大幅波动。花旗表示，期权市场的交易表明，投资者认为报告发布后的第二天股价可能会出现 9% 的波动。New Street Research 的 Pierre Ferragu 在“彭博监测”节目中谈到了他的预期。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/what-to-expect-from-nvidia-earnings-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 16:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
